File::RegexMatch - Extension to help find files using regular expressions.

Version 0.02

This is an easy-to-use file searching module. Further documentation can be found on the CPAN (http://search.cpan.org/~lloydg).

INSTALLATION

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

